          "_name": "article07",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article07\" group=\"Article\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Content Width\" name=\"contentWidth\" min=\"8\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"10\">\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Wrap Bg\" name=\"wrapBgColor\" value=\"#f7f7f7\">\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n      <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n      <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n      <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n    </fieldset>\n    <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n    <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.3\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n\n  <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n  <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\"></div>\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n      <div class=\"card col-md-12 col-lg-{{contentWidth}}\">\n        <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n          <h3 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style mbr-white mt-3 mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .card-box\"><b>Key Digital Safeguarding Laws</b></h3>\n          <div class=\"row card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n              <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>1. General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)</b></h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">The GDPR is a comprehensive data protection law implemented by the European Union in 2018. It sets strict guidelines for how personal data must be collected, stored, and processed. Key provisions include:<br><br><b>Consent :</b> Organizations must obtain explicit consent from individuals before&nbsp; &nbsp; collecting their data.<br><br><b>Right to Access : </b>Individuals have the right to access their data held by organizations.<br>\n<br><b>Right to be Forgotten :</b> Individuals can request the deletion of their data under certain&nbsp; conditions.<br>\n<br><b>Data Breach Notification :</b> Organizations must notify individuals and authorities of data breaches within 72 hours.<br><br>While GDPR primarily applies to EU citizens, its impact is global as it affects any organization handling EU residents’ data.<br></p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n              <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>2. California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA)</b></h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">The CCPA, enacted in 2020, is a landmark privacy law in the United States that grants California residents enhanced privacy rights and control over their personal information. Key aspects include:\n<br>\n<br><b>Right to Know : </b>Consumers can request information about the data collected about them and how it is used.<br>\n<br><b>Right to Delete : </b>Consumers can request the deletion of their personal information.<br>\n<br><b>Right to Opt-Out : </b>Consumers can opt out of the sale of their personal information.<br>\n<br><b>Non-Discrimination :</b> Businesses cannot discriminate against consumers for exercising their CCPA rights.<br><br>The CCPA sets a precedent for other states to follow and raises the standard for data privacy across the U.S.<br>\n<br>.</p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n              <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>3. Children’s Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA)</b></h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">COPPA is a U.S. federal law designed to protect the privacy of children under the age of 13. It requires websites and online services to obtain verifiable parental consent before collecting personal information from children. Key provisions include:\n<br>\n<br><b>Privacy Policies :</b> Websites must disclose their data collection practices.<br>\n<br><b>Parental Consent : </b>Parental consent must be obtained before collecting personal information from children.<br>\n<br><b>Access and Deletion : </b>Parents have the right to review and delete their children’s personal information.<br><br>COPPA aims to provide a safer online environment for children and ensure parents have control over their children’s data.</p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n              <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>4. Cybersecurity Information Sharing Act (CISA)</b></h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">CISA, enacted in the U.S. in 2015, encourages the sharing of cybersecurity threat information between the private sector and the government to improve collective cybersecurity. Key points include:\n<br>\n<br><b>Voluntary Sharing :</b> Organizations can voluntarily share cyber threat information with the government.<br><br><b>Protection from Liability :</b> Organizations are granted liability protection for sharing information in good faith.<br>\n<br><b>Privacy Protections :</b> Measures are in place to protect personal information during the sharing process.<br><br>CISA aims to enhance the nation’s ability to respond to and mitigate cyber threats.</p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">\n            <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Start Now</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "vdtMBSuWGQ",
          "_anchor": "article07-1x",
