          "_name": "features031",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features031\" group=\"Article\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen, 'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\" checked>\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Image\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <header>Card</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card BG\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card Color\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon Color\" name=\"iconColor\" value=\"#2a8cce\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#f2f2f2\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.7\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\"></div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showText\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 content-head mb-5\">\n                <h1 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style  mb-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Rise Of Online Communities\n</b><div><b><br></b></div></h1>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-4 mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">\n                    Great for pro-coders for fast prototyping and small customers' projects.\n                </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center  blockContent\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper align-left\">\n                    <div class=\"counter-container mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                        <ul>\n                            <li>The power of connectivity and the evolution of digital literacy have created a concept of forming an online community of the same interests, beliefs, and purpose. It has dismantled geographical challenges to connect and share ideas to foster better relationships among us. Whether it is a Facebook group of solo travelers or a discord server of video game enthusiasts, a sense of camaraderie and belonging is instilled in an increasingly fragmented world. Online communities for professionals of a niche have been able to provide their members with trending skills and updates. These communities offer access and inclusivity for equal opportunities to everyone.</li>\n                            <li>Online communities have also emerged as a tool to voice opinions for activism and social change. People can mobilize and amplify their stand on issues ranging from environmental change to human rights. Hikikomori, a term from Japan, describes a severe form of social withdrawal where individuals isolate themselves from society, often for months or even years. For Gen Z, this behavior is on the rise, driven by the very digital tools meant to keep them connected. The anonymity of the internet can sometimes breed cruelty, with cyberbullying becoming a major issue. Online communities that support mental health and encourage in-person engagement from time to time can tackle such issues in a society where everyone feels heard and safe both online and offline.</li>\n                        </ul>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                    <img class=\"w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-3.webp\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
