          "_name": "article22",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article22\" group=\"Article\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"reverseContent\" title=\"Reverse\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showButton\" title=\"Buttons\">\n    <header>Card</header>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card BG\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card Color\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#f7f7f7\" selected>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon Color\" name=\"iconColor\" value=\"#2a8cce\" selected>\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n      <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n      <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n      <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n    </fieldset>\n    <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n    <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.7\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n  <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n  <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\"></div>\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n      <div class=\"col-lg-4\">\n        <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n          <h5 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\"><b>Impact On Jobs And Technology\n</b><div><b><br></b></div></h5>\n          <h6 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle, .main-button\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><i>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</i><div><i>\n</i></div><div><br></div></h6>\n          <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer mt-3  main-button\" mbr-if=\"showButton\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n            <a href class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Learn More</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"col-lg-8 side-features\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper align-left\">\n          <div class=\"counter-container mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n            <ol>\n              <li>The concern of AI and automation taking over our jobs has been a real talking point in the last few years. Machine Learning (ML) possesses the capability of performing complex tasks that were once exclusive to humans and has restructured the employment landscape in the job market. An IMF report was presented in the recent meeting at Davos of the World Economic Forum which stated 40% of the jobs around the world will be affected by AI. In developed economies, around 60% of the jobs will be impacted by Machine Learning of which half will be negatively impacted</li><li>While economic forecasts have painted a dark picture of technology taking over us, the reality is more nuanced. The integration of AI and automation has led complex workplace factors to become more efficient. Organizations can focus on sustainability and growth by analyzing patterns from data. Empathy and organizational behavior have taken precedence over technical skills that can be performed by machines. Human action has been eliminated to a large extent in the user journey. Automation has helped marketing efforts to be tracked and analyzed for better performance. Marketers can shift their focus to authentic brand building and impacting the ecosystem, while automation software takes care of personalized advertising, behavioral targeting, and many other systems.</li>\n            </ol>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n\n\n\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "vdtU0j33MV",
