          "_name": "features030",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features030\" group=\"Article\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Image\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <header>Card</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card BG\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card Color\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon Color\" name=\"iconColor\" value=\"#2a8cce\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#f2f2f2\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.7\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\"></div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showText\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 content-head mb-5\">\n                <h1 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style  mb-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>A Digitally Empowered Society\n</b><div><b><br></b></div></h1>\n                <p class=\"mbr-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-4 mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-subtitle\">\n                    Great for pro-coders for fast prototyping and small customers' projects.\n                </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center  blockContent\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper align-left\">\n                    <div class=\"mbr-text counter-container mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                        <ol>\n                            <li><span style=\"font-size: 1.3rem;\">Digital literacy has been driving meaningful change in society with its broad spectrum of competencies like digital ethics, digital citizenship, and digital rights. These pillars lay the foundation of a digitally empowered society, where individuals can navigate and engage responsibly in the digital realm. Digital literacy emphasizes on importance of ethical norms for safeguarding privacy and data in this interconnected world. Digital literacy builds a culture of trust and collectiveness in online interactions contributing to an equitable digital ecosystem. Digital citizenship replicates the responsible and united behavior as of a citizen in a physical world. Societies can harness the collective wisdom and perspective of diverse members to address challenges and drive social progress through digital citizenship. Digital empowerment can only be achieved through the recognition and protection of digital rights. Digital literacy enables us to protect our right to privacy through different social apps, understand digital protection laws, demand transparency from tech apps on using our data, or advocate for digital accessibility.</span></li><li>The island country of Tuvalu becomes the first digital nation as it shifts its governance and administrative system to the metaverse. This low-lying island in the Pacific is predicted to be submerged by 02100 due to rising sea levels caused by climate change. Tuvalu intends to stay functioning irrespective if the island exists in the future or if its people migrate to different parts of the world. Tuvalu’s landscape will be preserved through a virtual twin for its cultural heritage and traditional beliefs to serve as a memory of its Indigenous people.</li>\n                        </ol>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                <div class=\"image-wrapper mb-4\">\n                    <img class=\"w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/empowering-nonprofit-digital-transformation-for-social-impact-banner.webp\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "vduoypQfG7",
          "_anchor": "features030-2o",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
