          "_name": "people04",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"people04\" plugins=\"Masonry\" group=\"People\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\t<mbr-parameters>\n\t\t<header>Size</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n\t\t<header>Show/Hide</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showMainTitle\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showMainSubtitle\">\n\t\t<header>Card</header>\n\t\t<select title=\"Columns\" name=\"columns\">\n\t\t\t<option value=\"12\">1</option>\n\t\t\t<option value=\"6\">2</option>\n\t\t\t<option value=\"4\" selected>3</option>\n\t\t\t<option value=\"3\">4</option>\n\t\t</select>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Image\" name=\"showImage\">\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Name\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Card BG\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n\t\t<header>Background</header>\n\t\t<fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n\t\t\t<input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n\t\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#2a8cce\" selected>\n\t\t</fieldset>\n\t\t\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t</mbr-parameters>\n\t<div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n\t</div>\n\t<div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"row mb-5 justify-content-center\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col-12 mb-0 content-head\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<b>Community Love</b><i><br>See What The Community Says About Datayug</i></h3>\n\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n\t\t\t\t\tList your customers' testimonials in this block.</h5>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"row mbr-masonry\" data-masonry=\"{&quot;percentPosition&quot;: true }\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}} active\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">On behalf of Junior Chamber International (JCI), I would like to extend our heartfelt appreciation to Data Yug for conducting the recent training session on Artificial Intelligence and Career Orientation at RB Anupchand Hindi School.<br>Your comprehensive insights into AI, coupled with career guidance, have made a significant impact on the participants.\n<br><br></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-wrapper mt-4 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/screenshot-2026-3.png\" alt=\"JCI SHILLONG PINE CITY\" data-slide-to=\"0\" data-bs-slide-to=\"0\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .img-wrapper\"><b>JCI Shillong Pine City</b></h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">The school acknowledges the conduct of a session on Cyber Bullying and Smartphone awareness on 06/07/2024 at BSF Sr Sec School, Shillong. The school extends a heartfelt gratitude to the team of Datayug Society for conducting such useful programme for the students\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-wrapper mt-4 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"../_images/people/team2.jpg\" data-slide-to=\"1\" data-bs-slide-to=\"1\" alt>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .img-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>BSF Senior Secondary School Umpling</b></h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">This is to state that, in commemoration of women's Day, the Datayug Society conducted a programme on Cyber Awareness I Hygiene on the 8th of March, 2025, in Lady Keane College.<br><br>The event was a timely and relevant one which benefitted both students and teachers. I wish the team every success.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-wrapper mt-4 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"../_images/people/team4.jpg\" data-slide-to=\"2\" data-bs-slide-to=\"2\" alt>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .img-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>Lady Keane College</b></h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">During my internship at Datayug Society, I worked on cybercrime awareness initiatives, from studying online threats to conducting programs in schools and communities. This strengthened my digital safety knowledge, improved my communication, teamwork, and confidence, and gave me practical skills for my future career.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-wrapper mt-4 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"../_images/people/team3.jpg\" data-slide-to=\"3\" data-bs-slide-to=\"3\" alt>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .img-wrapper\"><b>Jaisephin</b></h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">During this internship, I focused on creating impactful surveys and conducting in depth research to support our projects. I also had the opportunity to write a blog, which helped me strengthen my content writing skills. One of the most meaningful moments was delivering the vote of thanks at workshops an experience that built my confidence in public speaking and allowed me to express gratitude on behalf of our team.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-wrapper mt-4 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"../_images/people/team6.jpg\" data-slide-to=\"4\" data-bs-slide-to=\"4\" alt>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .img-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>Ibakordor</b></h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">My one month internship at Datayug Society was a chapter of growth, learning, and connection. I explored cybersecurity awareness, policy drafting, and research, while also creating presentations, designing posts, and facilitating workshops. The support of my mentors and colleagues made me feel valued, and the experience showed me how small efforts can create meaningful impact; a milestone I'll always cherish.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-wrapper mt-4 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"../_images/people/team2.jpg\" data-slide-to=\"5\" data-bs-slide-to=\"5\" alt>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .img-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>Rachelle</b></h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "vcJfuubuGE",
          "_anchor": "people04-8",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
