          "_name": "list01",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"list1\" group=\"List\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background':bg.parallax}\" plugins=\"mbr-switch-arrow, mobirise-icons2\">\t\n    <mbr-parameters>\n\t\t<header>Size</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n\t\t<header>Show/Hide</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n\t\t<select title=\"Amount\" name=\"cardAmount\">\n\t\t\t<option value=\"1\">1</option>\n\t\t\t<option value=\"2\">2</option>\n\t\t\t<option value=\"3\">3</option>\n\t\t\t<option value=\"4\">4</option>\n\t\t\t<option value=\"5\">5</option>\n\t\t\t<option value=\"6\" selected>6</option>\n\t\t</select>\n\t\t<header>Color</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Item\" name=\"items\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n\n\t\t<header>Background</header>\n\t\t<fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n\t\t\t<input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n\t\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#f7f7f7\" selected>\n\t\t</fieldset>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" checked condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.9\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t</mbr-parameters>\n\t<div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\"></div>\n\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-10 m-auto\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row justify-content-center mb-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showSubtitle\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-12 content-head\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"mbr-section-head\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>Got Questions?</b>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mt-4 mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFAQ</h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"bootstrap-accordion\" class=\"panel-group accordionStyles accordion\" role=\"tablist\" aria-multiselectable=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingOne\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse1\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse1\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-semibold mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWhat Is Datayug Society About?</h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sign mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-arrow-down\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"collapse1\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingOne\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"mbr-fonts-style panel-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">Datayug Society aims to build digital awareness and foster growth with new-age digital technologies. It works on bringing digital literacy to all age groups enabling people to access and reap benefits in their respective fields.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 1\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingOne\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse2\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse2\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-semibold mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWhy Should We Choose Datayug?</h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sign mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-arrow-down\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"collapse2\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingOne\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"mbr-fonts-style panel-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">The organization's objective is to empower the community with an integrated platform of digital literacy, education, and capacity programs. Datayug is on a mission to create sustainable development by generating awareness of digital marketing, banking technologies, cyber threats, upskilling, and personal development.</p><p></p><p></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 2\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingOne\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse3\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse3\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-semibold mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tWhat Time is The Office Open?</h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sign mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-arrow-down\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"collapse3\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingOne\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"mbr-fonts-style panel-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">Monday To Friday <b>11:30AM - 4:00PM</b></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 3\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingOne\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse4\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse4\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-semibold mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">Where Is The Office Located At?</h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sign mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-arrow-down\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"collapse4\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingOne\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"mbr-fonts-style panel-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\"><a href=\"https://maps.app.goo.gl/BN44nsQb1yViu1cD6\" class=\"text-primary\">Pythorumkhrah,Golflink, Behind The JN Stadium</a></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 4\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingOne\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse5\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse5\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-semibold mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tHow does Datayug help the affected individuals?</h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sign mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-arrow-down\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"collapse5\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingOne\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"mbr-fonts-style panel-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">We help victims launch their complaints against cybercrimes to the Meghalaya Cyber Cell Wing And provide necessary&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 5\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-header\" role=\"tab\" id=\"headingOne\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a role=\"button\" class=\"panel-title collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-core href=\"#collapse6\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"collapse6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h6 class=\"panel-title-edit mbr-semibold mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".panel-title-edit\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIs Datayug connected with the Meghalaya Cyber Cell?</h6>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"sign mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-arrow-down\"></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"collapse6\" class=\"panel-collapse noScroll collapse\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"headingOne\" data-parent=\"#accordion\" data-bs-parent=\"#accordion\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"mbr-fonts-style panel-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".panel-text\">Yes, Datayug Society is connected with the Meghalaya Cyber Cell.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</section>",
