          "_name": "features038",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features38\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen, 'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <select title=\"Amount\" name=\"cardAmount\">\n            <option value=\"1\">1</option>\n            <option value=\"2\" selected>2</option>\n            <option value=\"3\">3</option>\n        </select>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\" checked>\n        <header>Image</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"autoSize\" title=\"Auto Size\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Height\" name=\"imageHeight\" min=\"3\" max=\"6\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\" condition=\"autoSize\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg\">\n                <div class=\"text-wrapper align-left\">\n                    <h1 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Ensuring the Digital Wellness Of Generation Alpha</b><b><br></b></h1>\n                    <p class=\"mbr-text align-left mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Technology has revolutionized the way we live and communicate. However, excessive screen time and social media use can have detrimental effects on children’s mental and physical health, social skills, and academic performance.</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p></p>\n                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn align-left mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"digitalWellness.html#article11-1j\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Read More</a></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}} image-wrapper\">\n                <img class=\"w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/screenshot-2026-03-14.webp\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row row-reverse justify-content-center\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 1\">\n\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg\">\n                <div class=\"text-wrapper align-left\">\n                    <h1 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Understanding Digital Safeguarding Laws: Protecting the Public in the Digital Age</b></h1>\n                    <p class=\"mbr-text align-left mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">In our increasingly digital world, safeguarding personal information and maintaining privacy online are paramount concerns. With the rapid advancement of technology, the legal landscape has evolved to protect individuals and families from various digital threats. Understanding digital safeguarding laws is essential for navigating the internet safely and ensuring our digital rights are upheld. This blog will explore key digital safeguarding statutes and offer practical advice on leveraging these laws to protect yourself and your family.</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p></p>\n                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn align-left mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"digitalSafeguarding.html#article11-1v\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Read More</a></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}} image-wrapper\">\n                <img class=\"w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-1.webp\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\" mbr-if=\"cardAmount > 2\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg\">\n                <div class=\"text-wrapper align-left\">\n                    <h1 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>We think in images</b></h1>\n                    <p class=\"mbr-text align-left mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">\n                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec egestas massa vel nulla gravida\n                        pulvinar. Pellentesque habitant morbi tristique senectus et netus et malesuada fames ac turpis\n                        egestas.\n                    </p>\n                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn align-left mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Get started</a></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}} image-wrapper\">\n                <img class=\"w-100\" src=\"../_images/gallery/gallery02.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
